        &lt;seg xml:id="{ancestor::app/@xml:id}-{@wit}_end"/&gt;
    &lt;p eID="novel1_letter4_div4_p40"/&gt; &lt;p sID="novel1_letter4_div4_p41"/&gt; Frankenstein discovered that I 
